info.name: Comic planets [Tumblr dash theme]
info.description: Theme for your Tumblr dashboard, with custom 'new post' icons. "A sillier system refers to a star and all the objects that tumble in orbit around it. Our sillier system consists of the sun - our star - eight comic planets and their nutty satellites (such as our moon); dwarf planets; asteroids and comics. Our sillier system is located in an awkward spiral of the Miltie's Way galaxy." †
